g.text: Virtual whiteboard for connecting hand-drawn like diagrams
Creating the Obsidian-Excalidraw plugin and its accompanying content
demands more time and dedication than one might expect. If you find
this tool valuable, consider supporting its growth and maintenance by
buying me a coffee on Ko-Fi.
